The YonMaster extension expands the automation capabilities for Chrome. It facilitates the native detection of UI elements when designing automation for web applications using YonMaster RPA Studio.

This extension is part of a solution and only works together with YonMaster RPA. To install YonMaster RPA, visit https://rpa.yonyoucloud.com.
